{"tid":1389404,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"天文台會在中午至下午二時考慮改發八號烈風或暴風信號。","createTime":"2019-07-31T01:50:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T02:27:45.000Z","uid":26298,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"2991ca0368198bf43b0bada31c991e7b20f3eed8","tid":1389404,"uid":26298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T01:50:02.000Z","msg":"最新風暴消息<br />\n<br />\n過去數小時，韋帕採取較偏北路徑移動。按照現時預測路徑，韋帕今日會逐漸靠近廣東西部沿岸，並於今日稍後最接近本港，在香港西南300公里左右掠過。預料下午本港風力會有所增強，天文台會在中午至下午二時考慮改發八號烈風或暴風信號。<br />\n<br />\n與韋帕相關的雨帶會為本港帶來大驟雨及狂風，海面亦會有大浪及湧浪，市民應該遠離岸邊及低窪地區，並停止所有水上活動。<br />\n<br />\n在過去一小時，橫瀾島、大老山及長洲泳灘分別錄得的最高持續風速為每小時66、62及57公里，最高陣風分別為每小時82、82及85公里。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hko.gov.hk/contentc.htm#\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hko.gov.hk%2Fcontentc.htm%23&d=z0v15oAQEaIuorZt047IjwwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=99ad8268\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hko.gov.hk/contentc.htm#</a>"},{"pid":"6af151d4be86aa9ac1725be39aef2fdba2dd655c","tid":1389404,"uid":63952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T01:53:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ab8b122c1fce2b06b8d309a12b3930606ea8656","tid":1389404,"uid":205710,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T01:56:13.000Z","msg":"各位義士留意，天文台話中午會可能會掛八號，請大家注意安全<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b09a31049d06d3b9239f28387b5a0ccb15b15487","tid":1389404,"uid":26298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T01:56:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a075ae5b8f230a3f0a744ee949f35ea64a8ea90b","tid":1389404,"uid":61173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T01:57:17.000Z","msg":"<img